review 1: I love the taste of satay's seasoning. It's peanut sauce is mouth watering since it is different from other satay's stall. The price is quite cheap and even you can ask for smaller portion if you want to. However, the place is not spacious enough, not too wide, but we can still order the food and take a dine there. There is no special parking area for any cars or motorbikes, just put your vehicle at the edge side of the street. It is better to take away the satay.
